# ============================================================
# math.ese — Mathematical Vocabulary for FLUX-san
# गणितशब्दावली — प्रवाहिनी भाषा सार्वभौमिक निष्पादनम्
# ============================================================
#
# Sanskrit mathematical terminology mapped to FLUX operations.
# Each entry: IAST term | Devanāgarī | FLUX opcode | English

# --- Arithmetic Operations (गणितक्रियाः) ---

# Addition (योगः)
gaṇaya    | गणय      | IADD     | add / compute sum
pluta     | प्लुत     | IADD     | plus (with)
yogaḥ     | योगः     | IADD     | sum / union
saṃyogaḥ  | संयोगः   | IADD     | conjunction / addition
rāśiyogaḥ | राशियोगः  | IADD     | sum of quantities

# Subtraction (व्यवकलनम्)
śoṣa      | शोष      | ISUB     | subtract / diminish
viśeṣaḥ   | विशेषः   | ISUB     | difference
apahāraḥ  | अपहारः   | ISUB     | removal / subtraction

# Multiplication (गुणनम्)
guṇa      | गुण      | IMUL     | multiply
guṇayogaḥ | गुणयोगः  | IMUL     | product
ghātaḥ    | घातः     | IMUL     | product (formal)
sarvasaṅkhyā | सर्वसङ्ख्या | IMUL | total multiplication

# Division (भाजनम्)
bhāj      | भाज      | IDIV     | divide
bhāgaḥ    | भागः     | IDIV     | division / share
bhājanaḥ  | भाजनम्   | IDIV     | act of dividing
hāraḥ     | हारः     | IDIV     | divisor

# Modulo (शेषः)
śeṣaḥ     | शेषः     | IMOD     | remainder
avaśiṣṭaḥ | अवशिष्टः | IMOD     | what remains

# Negation (विपर्ययः)
viparyayaḥ | विपर्ययः | INEG     | negate

# Increment / Decrement (वृद्धिः / ह्रासः)
pluta     | प्लुत     | INC      | increment / increase
hrāsaḥ    | ह्रासः    | DEC      | decrement / decrease

# --- Comparison (तुलना) ---

tulya     | तुल्य     | ICMP     | equal / compare
alpa      | अल्प      | ILT      | less than
bahutaraḥ | बहुतरः   | IGT      | greater than
samānaḥ   | समानः    | IEQ      | equal to

# --- Range / Accumulation ---

paryantayogaḥ | पर्यन्तयोगः | LOOP+IADD | sum from ... to ...
kramaśaḥ    | क्रमशः     | LOOP     | sequentially / step by step

# --- Power / Root (वर्ग / मूल) ---

vargaḥ     | वर्गः     | IMUL+IMUL | square
ghanaḥ     | घनः       | POW      | cube
mūlaḥ      | मूलः      | SQRT     | square root
gatau      | गतौ       | POW      | raised to

# --- Constants (स्थिराङ्काः) ---

pi         | पि        | CONST    | π (3.14159...)
e          | ए         | CONST    | Euler's e (2.71828...)
śūnyaḥ     | शून्यः    | MOVI 0   | zero
ekam       | एकम्     | MOVI 1   | one

# --- Number Words (सङ्ख्याशब्दाः) ---

śūnya  | शून्य   | 0
eka    | एक     | 1
dvi    | द्वि    | 2
tri    | त्रि    | 3
catur  | चतुर्  | 4
pañca  | पञ्च    | 5
ṣaṭ    | षट्    | 6
sapta  | सप्त    | 7
aṣṭa   | अष्ट   | 8
nava   | नव     | 9
daśa   | दश     | 10
viṃśati | विंशति | 20
śata   | शत     | 100
sahasra | सहस्र  | 1000
lakṣa  | लक्ष   | 100000
koṭi   | कोटि   | 10000000

# --- Stack Operations (स्तरक्रियाः) ---

juṣa     | जुष      | PUSH     | push onto stack
gṛhṇa   | गृह्ण    | POP      | pop from stack

# --- Registers / Memory (अवस्थायाः) ---

avasthā  | अवस्था   | REGISTERS | register state
sthāna   | स्थान    | MOVI     | place / location
sthira   | स्थिर    | STORE    | store (persist)

# --- Flow Control (प्रवाहनियन्त्रणम्) ---

āvṛttaḥ  | आवृत्तः  | JMP      | loop / repeat
yady      | यदि      | JZ/JE    | if (conditional)
anyathā   | अन्यथा   | JNE      | else (alternative)
virāmaḥ   | विरामः   | HALT     | halt / stop
darśaya   | दर्शय    | PRINT    | display / print
